<p>Forest monitoring and change detection systems employ remote sensing data provided by optical satellite sensors due to the availability of open access time-series data of global coverage. The aim of this talk was to highlight the 3D Modeling techniques for Forest Monitoring.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

