<p>Object Detection and Recognition training is to acquaint the learners with theoretical and practical knowledge of Object Detection &amp; Recognition, and its interesting applications. The workshop will help the participants get a deep dive into the underlying architecture and algorithms and get hands-on experience with the training of deep learning models. &nbsp;</p>
